Supabase provides a globally distributed cluster of Realtime servers that enable the following functionality:

- [Broadcast](${X.DOCS_URL}/guides/realtime/broadcast): Send ephemeral messages from client to clients with low latency.
- [Presence](${X.DOCS_URL}/guides/realtime/presence): Track and synchronize shared state between clients.
